        // read from: aWindLaneA, aWindLaneB, aScrapLaneB, aWindLaneC, aWindLaneD, aScrapLaneA, aWaterLaneC, aWaterLaneD, aSnowLaneA, aSnowLaneB, aSnowLaneC
